Mastering his media savvy, Trump orchestrated a significant shift in the American consciousness.For Trump, even the EU and Nato were objects of disdain. As far as politics goes, Donald Trump literally came from nowhere, and beat establishment figures like Hillary Clinton. Then it went so horribly wrong, both for him as a leader, but also for the country he turned into a laughing stock.
The much-lauded inexperience in matters Washington, first seen as a breath of fresh air, turns out to be his Achilles’ heel. From the outset, when he held up his first executive orders with a triumphant grin, the scene was set for a roller-coaster autocratic and shambolic leadership ride fed by a streak of incurable narcissism.



